Full Description: My 12-Fruits LLC is a trade unit of Colours of Africa. Colours of Africa LLC is at heart, a fair trade company, and we exist to bridge the gap that exists between African products and the American market. My 12-Fruits LLC is a groundbreaking startup that aims to foster the blooming and flourishing of black individuals, drawing inspiration from the resilience and strength of trees. We are deeply committed to preserving and celebrating the black culture, its diverse heritage, and the profound connections to our ancestral backgrounds. At My 12-Fruits, our primary mission is to provide a comprehensive platform for black individuals to explore and embrace their roots, even in cases where lineage has been lost or forgotten over time. Through our innovative technology and dedicated community, we empower every black man and woman to uncover the invaluable stories and traditions that shape their identity. Our journey began as BURUGI, but we recognised the need to evolve and expand our vision. My 12-Fruits represents the collective essence of our mission, symbolizing growth, nourishment, and unity within the black community. We firmly believe that by connecting individuals with their tribes, cultures, and family lineages, we strengthen the fabric of our collective identity. Our platform serves as a vibrant hub where both young and old can come together, fostering intergenerational dialogue and knowledge exchange. Through engaging interactions and collaborative initiatives, we enable young people to access a wealth of information about their heritage. From exploring oral histories and folklore to delving into genealogical records and historical archives, My 12-Fruits provides the tools and resources necessary for a deep understanding of one's cultural lineage. Recognising the urgent need to preserve the endangered black native culture, we stand as a guardian of knowledge. Our platform brings together historians, scholars, and individuals with profound insights into the black man's journey throughout history. We provide a platform for these knowledge holders to share their expertise, ensuring that their wisdom and narratives are passed down to future generations. In addition to our educational endeavours, My 12-Fruits offers a comprehensive eCommerce store, where individuals can explore and purchase a wide range of African cultural accessories. Each item is carefully curated to showcase the beauty, craftsmanship, and symbolism that embodies the richness of African heritage. By wearing and adorning themselves with these meaningful symbols, individuals can proudly display their connection to their roots. As a company deeply rooted in the empowerment of the black community, we are dedicated to creating lasting social impact. We actively collaborate with nonprofit organisations, educational institutions, and community leaders to drive positive change and support initiatives that uplift black voices. Join us on our mission to cultivate a world where black individuals thrive, rooted in their heritage and empowered by their culture. Together, let's build a future where the invaluable legacy of the black community flourishes, bringing unity, understanding, and pride to all.
Industry Groups: Advertising, Commerce and Shopping, Education, Other, Sales and Marketing

Full Description: Avox helps clients in the global financial services industry manage and maintain true and accurate legal entity data. Avox validates, corrects, enriches and maintains business entity reference data. This includes data such as corporate hierarchies, registered address information, industry sector codes and company identifiers. The company was founded in 2003 in cooperation with several financial institutions that required a more efficient mechanism for improving data quality and timeliness. The Avox operational model is unique in the industry. Its success stems from the continuous sharing of business intelligence with its clients and partners which Avox centralizes, anonymizes, verifies and publishes out to each participant. Financial institutions participating in Avox form a Community that collectively addresses poor client, issuer and counterparty data quality. The Community participants, which include some of the largest banks and asset managers in the world, both contribute and subscribe to a shared pool of data, processes and resources. Avox was voted “Best Counterparty Data Provider of the Year” for both 2009 and 2010.

Headquarters Regions: Greater Miami Area, East Coast, Southern US
Full Description: Youcode.com is a website that allows members to meet new people whom they have seen out in public. Youcode.com helps members meet and interact with people in the Real World. Youcode.com provides its users with three ways to connect with others in public.  The first is called Meet Me.  With Meet Me, Youcode users indicate where they are located.  If multiple users indicate that they are hanging out at the same location, a listing of profiles is displayed allowing the members to message each other.  Meet Me is specifically designed for use with Apple's iPhone. The second method to meet new friends is by displaying a TAG.  A TAG is a sticker printed with a graphical representation of an activity that interests the member and can be used by others to search for the member's profile on Youcode.com.  A TAG can be publicly displayed wherever others will see it.  The third method to meet new friends is by handing out personalized cards printed with the member's unique Youcode.  The cards can be used by others to contact the member via Youcode.com.  Because only the Youcode is printed on the card, members protect their personal information such as email, phone number and address from others. New members receive a free welcome packet containing products developed by Moo.com and Makestickers.com personalized with their Youcode and TAG. Youcode supports various charitable organizations and likes to call what they do Social Interaction infused with Social Responsibility.
